headline: GE Q3 Deep Dive: Service Growth and Supply Chain Progress Drive Results Amid Margin Compression
summary: Industrial conglomerate GE Aerospace (NYSE:GE) reported Q3 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 36.2% year on year to $12.18 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.66 per share was 13% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
